OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,F"Significant failures" in police
OL,7,Fleadership and social media
OL,8,Fmisinformation led to violent disorder
OL,9,Fin Leicester in 2022, a report has
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FThe report, led by the School of
OL,13,FOriental and African Studies (SOAS) in
OL,14,FLondon, looks at how tensions which
OL,15,Farose between communities in the
OL,16,Fcity's South Asian diaspora in May
OL,17,Fthat year escalated into major
OL,18,Fdisorder in August and September.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
