FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,FYoung men mainly from parts of the
OL,7,FMuslim and Hindu communities were
OL,8,Finvolved spates of vandalism, assaults
OL,9,Fand attacks on places of worship and
OL,10,Fproperties in Leicester.
OL,12,FWhile the exact cause of the unrest
OL,13,Fwas unclear, the report alludes to the
OL,14,F2022 Asia Cup cricket match between
OL,15,FPakistan and India on 28 August as
OL,16,Fpart of the sequence of events while
OL,17,Ftensions escalated.
OL,19,FWhat the report found
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,FThe report found the responses from
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police and Leicester
OL,8,FCity Council were "lacking or
OL,9,Finconsistent," with "major gaps in
OL,10,Fintelligence, communication, and
OL,11,Fvisible and active civic leadership."
OL,13,FIt also found social media
OL,14,F"misinformation" and "fear messaging"
OL,15,Fplayed a "key role in generating
OL,16,Fmistrust and hostility" between the
OL,17,Ftwo groups.
OL,19,FDozens of people were arrested by
OL,20,FLeicestershire Police in connection
OL,21,Fwith the disorder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,FThe government has commissioned an
OL,7,Findependent review into the disorder,
OL,8,Fwhich will consider the findings from
OL,9,Fthe SOAS report in its conclusions.
OL,11,FThe report author, Professor Juan
OL,12,FMendez, said: "The events of 2022 were
OL,13,Fdeeply traumatic for many residents,
OL,14,Fbut we met many people who have high
OL,15,Fhopes for all communities in Leicester
OL,16,Fco-existing peacefully.
OL,18,F"Much depends on how young people work
OL,19,Fbetter together.
OL,26,@tD@BrrtD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
