OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,F"Our report is not about apportioning
OL,7,Fblame but understanding how tensions
OL,8,Fescalated, why safeguards failed, and
OL,9,Fhow trust can be rebuilt through fair
OL,10,Fand accountable action."
OL,12,FWhat the police said
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
