PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,F"We also continue to use dedicated
OL,7,Fcommunication channels such as
OL,8,FNeighbourhood Link and WhatsApp groups
OL,9,Fto keep residents informed about local
OL,10,Fpriorities, to counter misinformation,
OL,11,Fto increase public trust and
OL,12,Fconfidence."
OL,14,FLeicester City Mayor, Sir Peter
OL,15,FSoulsby, said: "I haven't yet received
OL,16,Fa copy of their report but will
OL,17,Fobviously look carefully at what they
OL,18,Fhave to say.
OL,26,@tD@LO]wD@POU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
