OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771876127
OL,3,C'Significant failures' in policing led
OL,4,Cto violent disorder, report finds
OL,6,F"When they began their research,
OL,7,Fnearly three years ago, I did raise
OL,8,Fsome questions with them about their
OL,9,Findependence, who had commissioned
OL,10,Fthem, and how they were going to take
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,F"I didn't get a convincing
OL,14,Fexplanation. I don't know who they
OL,15,Fhave spoken to."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
